	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I finished some animation on the shields. Here's what some gameplay looks like (just me controlling Player 1...)<br /><br />The shields follow their respective player (but slower than the player moves). Each player can temporarily stop their shield so they can peak around it and hit the opponent.<br /><br />Also, I think I've decided to change the name of the game to &quot;LightShields&quot;, since Spong seems to confuse people and Pong is a trademark.<br /><br /><div class="attachtitle">Attachment:</div><div class="attachcontent">
			<img src="./download/file.php?id=10838" alt="spong-animations.gif" /><br />
