		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Just opened it to check out, couldn't play properly since I was alone, but - <br /><br />If the other player never moves, you can't kill them! Maybe you could fix this by adding a short refractory period to the shields, so they would be down for a second after being hit. <br /><br />Just a thought!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
