	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">toggle switch wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Maybe you could fix this by adding a short refractory period to the shields, so they would be down for a second after being hit.</div><br />That's a good idea.<br />I've toyed with randomly appearing extra-life powerups to encourage players to move around, but that tended to stretch the game on pretty long.<br />My next thought was to make the shield shrink if the player has been sitting still for a while, but I like the idea of making the shield ineffective for a couple seconds after being hit.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
